      <bioghist id="aspace_346443fc9bfb0793fb21c37c593a0f65">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>
            <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
               <part>The Yale Scientific Monthly</part>
            </title> was published by the senior class of the Sheffield Scientific School, Yale University, from 1894-1913. In 1913, the title was changed to the <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
               <part>Yale Sheffield Monthly</part>
            </title>, which was superseded by the <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
               <part>Yale Graphic</part>
            </title> in 1919.</p>
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_fbc4a44a3ddabf5b97e31f9a469993bb">
